Package: LAWSHiC
Title: Local Adaptive Weighted Smoothing for Hi-C Interaction Calling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Lingbo", "Zhou", email = "lbzhou1998@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Identifies significant chromatin interactions in Hi-C data by estimating
    the local null proportion pi(i,j) for each bin pair via a multi-tau Gaussian
    kernel smoother, then applying weighted Benjamini-Hochberg FDR control.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.14.0),
    foreach,
    doParallel,
    parallel
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
